This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computation and Language (cs.CL) as it deals with Neural Machine Translation (NMT) models and their performance. It could also belong to the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it involves training models using large sets of data. Additionally, it could be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves the use of machine translation models. Neural Networks (cs.NE) and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) could also be possible categories as NMT models are a type of neural network and the paper involves analyzing the performance of models.
